title: FTX's Debtors Revise Settlement Proposal After Objection From U.S. Trustee
description: Bankrupt crypto exchange FTX's debtors have revised their motion for settlement after the U.S. Trustee objected to an earlier motion.

title: Farmington Bank Faces Fed Wrath: Alameda-Backed Financial Institution Ordered to Shutdown
description: In a statement released August 17, 2023, Farmington State Bank, with an investment from Sam Bankman-Fried’s Alameda Research, consented to a cease and desist order from the U.S. Federal Reserve.
